name: WritersBlock

skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: writer's block
des: Writer's block is a whispered curse that afflicts even the best of us. It makes us want to do anything but writing, while we wait aimlessly, hoping beyond hope that inspiration comes to us one random day as we site on the couch. This Alexa skill reads out inspirational quotes from actual writers about writers' block, to help you get going again!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
